value.name: Untitled Little House on the Prairie Reboot
value.original_name: Untitled Little House on the Prairie Reboot
value.overview: Part hopeful family drama, part epic survival tale, and part origin story of the American West, this fresh adaptation of Laura Ingalls Wilder's iconic semi-autobiographical 'Little House' books offers a kaleidoscopic view of the struggles and triumphs of those who shaped the frontier.
